			<h3 class="_fw600">Examples</h3>
			<p>Below are some examples of content not allowed on Mockering.</p>
			<ul>
				<li>A video that shows minors participating in provocative, sexually or sexually suggestive activities, challenges and courage (such as kissing or groping).</li>
				<li>Show minors who are involved in hazardous activities, such as physical stunts, the use of weapons or explosives, or the use of controlled substances such as alcohol or nicotine.</li>
				<li>Videos labeled "for children" contain family-friendly cartoons, involving improper behavior such as injection needles.</li>
			</ul>
			<p>Please keep in mind that these are just some examples, if you think the content may violate this policy, do not post the content.</p>
